---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base
  title="Projects"
  description="Portfolio: Jules AI system, personality assessments, Discord server management, websites, and developer utilities."
>
  <div class="container">
    <h1>Projects</h1>

    <div class="project-card">
      <h3><a href="/jules/">Jules AI Collaborator</a></h3>
      <span class="status">Live</span>
      <p>
        Open-source AI operational system that runs my business. Content pipelines, research, scheduling, reporting, code. Built on Claude Code with 18 custom skills, 5 hooks, cloud batch automation, and mobile access.
      </p>
      <p><a href="/jules/">How it works &rarr;</a> &middot; <a href="https://github.com/jonathanmalkin/jules">GitHub &rarr;</a></p>
    </div>

    <div class="project-card">
      <h3><a href="https://quiz.9archetypes.app">9 Archetypes Quiz</a></h3>
      <span class="status">Live</span>
      <p>
        Interactive personality assessment that identifies relationship and communication styles across 9 archetypes for adult audiences. React + TypeScript frontend, PHP + MySQL backend. Personalized email playbooks, partner comparison, and post-quiz survey. 200+ daily users.
      </p>
      <p><a href="https://quiz.9archetypes.app">Take the quiz &rarr;</a></p>
    </div>

    <div class="project-card">
      <h3>Discord Server Manager</h3>
      <span class="status">Archived</span>
      <p>
        Suite of tools for running a 300+ member community server. Automated onboarding and verification, role assignment, and moderation tracking. Analytics dashboard with DAU/WAU/MAU tracking, engagement funnels, daily and weekly health reports, and dead channel detection. Permissions explorer evaluating Discord's 7-layer permission hierarchy via slash commands. DM export tool for archival. Python + TypeScript.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="project-card">
      <h3><a href="https://github.com/jonathanmalkin/builtwithjon">Websites</a></h3>
      <span class="status">Live</span>
      <p>
        builtwithjon.com and supporting sites. Astro v6 static generation, zero JavaScript, hand-written CSS under 5KB. Cloudflare Workers auto-deploy on push. SEO layer with JSON-LD structured data, sitemap, RSS feed, and llms.txt for AI extraction. Full-stack web: static site generation, CDN hosting, domain management, email routing.
      </p>
      <p><a href="https://github.com/jonathanmalkin/builtwithjon">GitHub &rarr;</a></p>
    </div>

    <div class="project-card">
      <h3>Utilities</h3>
      <span class="status">Mixed</span>
      <p>
        <strong>Whisper Repetition Fix:</strong> Homebrew wrapper intercepting whisper-cli calls with anti-repetition flags — entropy thresholds, context limiting, non-speech suppression. Companion Python post-processor with 90+ hallucination pattern filters, n-gram dedup, and optional Claude Haiku fallback.
      </p>
      <p>
        <strong>Event Distribution System:</strong> Full-stack TypeScript app for AI-powered event creation (ChatGPT themes + DALL-E banners) with automated posting to 6 platforms — WordPress, Facebook, Instagram, Eventbrite, Meetup, and FetLife. RSVP management with location gating.
      </p>
      <p>
        <strong>Plane Sync:</strong> Bidirectional markdown-to-Plane.so sync with cursor pagination, state reconciliation, and 1Password credential management.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</Base>
